Package lexparse

Class KnightCodeBaseVisitor<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.AbstractParseTreeVisitor<T>
      • lexparse.KnightCodeBaseVisitor<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The return type of the visit operation. Use Void for operations with no return type.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    KnightCodeVisitor<T>, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeVisitor<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    KnightVisitor
    public class KnightCodeBaseVisitor<T>
extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.AbstractParseTreeVisitor<T>
implements KnightCodeVisitor<T>
    This class provides an empty implementation of KnightCodeVisitor, which can be extended to create a visitor which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
